<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Tajikistan: OMRI - 3JAN97 - TERRORISM IN TAJIK CAPITAL</title>
<h1>OMRI - 3JAN97 - TERRORISM IN TAJIK CAPITAL</h1>
<i>eurasia@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Mon, 06 Jan 97 14:48:37 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
