<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Tajikistan: OMRI - 2JAN97 - TAJIK-IRANIAN RELATIONS</title>
<h1>OMRI - 2JAN97 - TAJIK-IRANIAN RELATIONS</h1>
<i>eurasia@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Mon, 06 Jan 97 14:40:46 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#75">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#75">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#75">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#75">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
