<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Tajikistan: Interfax 26Dec96 Tajik Group Frees Joint Commission Member</title>
<h1>Interfax 26Dec96 Tajik Group Frees Joint Commission Member</h1>
<i>fsu@mail.sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Mon, 30 Dec 96 16:00:32 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#73">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#73">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#73">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#73">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0074.html">fsu@mail.sorosny.org: "Interfax 29Dec96 Rakhmonov Issues Privatization Decree"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0072.html">fsu@mail.sorosny.org: "Interfax 23Dec96, Tajik Govt &amp; Opposition Sign Moscow Accord"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
