<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Tajikistan: OMRI - 13DEC96 - TAJIK CEASEFIRE VIOLATED IN FIRST 24 HOURS</title>
<h1>OMRI - 13DEC96 - TAJIK CEASEFIRE VIOLATED IN FIRST 24 HOURS</h1>
<i>eurasia@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Fri, 13 Dec 96 11:45:45 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#66">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#66">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#66">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#66">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0067.html">fsu@mail.sorosny.org: "Interfax-13 Dec. Tajik Opposition Kills 4, Wounds 14 Troops"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0065.html">eurasia@sorosny.org: "MORI - 13DEC96 - YURII BATURIN IN TAJIKISTAN"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
