<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Tajikistan: MORI - 13DEC96 - YURII BATURIN IN TAJIKISTAN</title>
<h1>MORI - 13DEC96 - YURII BATURIN IN TAJIKISTAN</h1>
<i>eurasia@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Fri, 13 Dec 96 11:44:58 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#65">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#65">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#65">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#65">[ author ]</a>
