<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Tajikistan: OMRI - 5DEC96 - TAJIK FIGHTING CONTINUES, MOVES CLOSER TO CA</title>
<h1>OMRI - 5DEC96 - TAJIK FIGHTING CONTINUES, MOVES CLOSER TO CA</h1>
<i>eurasia@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Thu, 05 Dec 96 14:25:42 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#58">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#58">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#58">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#58">[ author ]</a>
