<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Tajikistan: OMRI - 11Nov96 - Tajik Opposition Releases Prisoners</title>
<h1>OMRI - 11Nov96 - Tajik Opposition Releases Prisoners</h1>
<i>eurasia@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Mon, 11 Nov 96 15:36:29 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#47">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#47">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#47">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#47">[ author ]</a>
