<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Tajikistan: OMRI--4 Nov 1996-TAJIK OPPOSITION RELEASES 10 HOSTAGES</title>
<h1>OMRI--4 Nov 1996-TAJIK OPPOSITION RELEASES 10 HOSTAGES</h1>
<i>eurasia@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Mon, 04 Nov 96 11:49:33 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#43">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#43">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#43">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#43">[ author ]</a>
