<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Tajikistan: OMRI--1 Nov 1996-CENTRAL ASIANS AT DONOR CONFERENCE IN JAPAN</title>
<h1>OMRI--1 Nov 1996-CENTRAL ASIANS AT DONOR CONFERENCE IN JAPAN</h1>
<i>arichter@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Sun, 03 Nov 96 13:36:11 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#42">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#42">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#42">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#42">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0043.html">eurasia@sorosny.org: "OMRI--4 Nov 1996-TAJIK OPPOSITION RELEASES 10 HOSTAGES"</a>
