<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Tajikistan: OMRI--1 October 1996 -CENTRAL ASIA VOICES CONCERN OVER KABUL</title>
<h1>OMRI--1 October 1996 -CENTRAL ASIA VOICES CONCERN OVER KABUL</h1>
<i>eurasia@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Tue, 01 Oct 96 12:21:40 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#30">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#30">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#30">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#30">[ author ]</a>
