     establish an Islamic regime in Tajikistan, Russian and Western <br>
     agencies reported on 7 September. At the same time, he declare that <br>
     "we respect" Islam as a "base of moral and spiritual cleanliness and <br>
     source of culture," Reuters reported. The f<br>
