<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Tajikistan: OMRI--29 August 96--RUSSIA, TAJIKISTAN GIVEN OBSERVER STATUS</title>
<h1>OMRI--29 August 96--RUSSIA, TAJIKISTAN GIVEN OBSERVER STATUS</h1>
<i>tlankina@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Fri, 30 Aug 96 09:19:46 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#17">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#17">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#17">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#17">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0018.html">eurasia@mail.sorosny.org: "OMRI--30 August 1996--Border Guard Officers Confer"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0016.html">tlankina@sorosny.org: "OMRI--29 August 96--WHO CONTROLS WHAT IN TAJIKISTAN"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
