<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Uzbekistan: OMRI - 21Nov96 - Kazakstan Agrees with Uzbekistan, Kyrgyzsta</title>
<h1>OMRI - 21Nov96 - Kazakstan Agrees with Uzbekistan, Kyrgyzsta</h1>
<i>eurasia@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Thu, 21 Nov 96 11:41:02 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#54">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#54">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#54">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#54">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0055.html">eurasia@sorosny.org: "OMRI - 26Nov96 - UZBEK PARLIAMENT OPENS WITH HUMAN RIGHTS AG"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0053.html">eurasia@sorosny.org: "OMRI - 19Nov96 - Uzbekistan, Kazakstan Sign Gas Deal"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
</ul>
<!-- body="start" -->
     <br>
     KAZAKSTAN AGREES WITH UZBEKISTAN, KYRGYZSTAN ON GAS DEBTS. Kazakstan <br>
     has signed an agreement with Uzbekistan in Tashkent on paying off its <br>
     $24 million debt for Uzbek gas, Kazakhstanskaya pravda reported on 19 <br>
     November. In October, Uzbekistan withheld gas deliveries due to <br>
     nonpayments and the Kazakstani capital, Almaty, received only half of <br>
     what it needed for that month, leading to a severe gas deficiency in <br>
     many households. Besides direct monetary compensation to pay for Uzbek <br>
     gas, Kazakstan also offered to supply gas from Caspian Sea regions of <br>
     Kazakstan to western Uzbekistan. Kazakstan is also close to completing <br>
     a deal with Kyrgyzstan on electricity supplies to southern Kazakstan. <br>
     The Kyrgyz have agreed to defer Kazakstan's $8 million debt for Kyrgyz <br>
     electricity but prices for electricity will now be higher. -- Slava <br>
     Kozlov in Almaty and Bruce Pannier<br>
<!-- body="end" -->
<p>
<ul>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0055.html">eurasia@sorosny.org: "OMRI - 26Nov96 - UZBEK PARLIAMENT OPENS WITH HUMAN RIGHTS AG"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0053.html">eurasia@sorosny.org: "OMRI - 19Nov96 - Uzbekistan, Kazakstan Sign Gas Deal"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
</ul>
