<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Uzbekistan: OMRI - 15Nov96 - Monetary Crisis Worsens in Uzbekistan</title>
<h1>OMRI - 15Nov96 - Monetary Crisis Worsens in Uzbekistan</h1>
<i>eurasia@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Thu, 14 Nov 96 13:02:00 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#52">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#52">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#52">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#52">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0053.html">eurasia@sorosny.org: "OMRI - 19Nov96 - Uzbekistan, Kazakstan Sign Gas Deal"</a>
