<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Uzbekistan: OMRI--1 Nov 1996-CENTRAL ASIANS AT DONOR CONFERENCE IN JAPAN</title>
<h1>OMRI--1 Nov 1996-CENTRAL ASIANS AT DONOR CONFERENCE IN JAPAN</h1>
<i>arichter@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Sun, 03 Nov 96 13:36:11 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#47">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#47">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#47">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#47">[ author ]</a>
