<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Uzbekistan: OMRI--Oct 31--NEW POLITICAL OFFICE CREATED IN UZBEKISTAN</title>
<h1>OMRI--Oct 31--NEW POLITICAL OFFICE CREATED IN UZBEKISTAN</h1>
<i>arichter@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Thu, 31 Oct 96 13:07:35 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#45">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#45">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#45">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#45">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
