<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Uzbekistan: OMRI--29 Oct 1996--POLITICAL HEADS ROLL IN UZBEKISTAN</title>
<h1>OMRI--29 Oct 1996--POLITICAL HEADS ROLL IN UZBEKISTAN</h1>
<i>arichter@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Tue, 29 Oct 96 11:32:22 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#43">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#43">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#43">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#43">[ author ]</a>
