<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Uzbekistan: OMRI--21 Oct 1996--PAKISTAN'S PRESIDENT VISITS UZBEKISTAN</title>
<h1>OMRI--21 Oct 1996--PAKISTAN'S PRESIDENT VISITS UZBEKISTAN</h1>
<i>arichter@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Mon, 21 Oct 96 12:05:16 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#39">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#39">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#39">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#39">[ author ]</a>
