<h1>OMRI--Oct 14 1996--RUSSIA ASSESSES UZBEK'S AFGHAN RESPONSE.</h1>
<i>eurasia@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Mon, 14 Oct 96 16:15:00 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#35">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#35">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#35">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#35">[ author ]</a>
