<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Uzbekistan: OMRI--10 October 1996--UZBEK MEDIA SHOOTS BACK</title>
<h1>OMRI--10 October 1996--UZBEK MEDIA SHOOTS BACK</h1>
<i>eurasia@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Thu, 10 Oct 96 11:02:08 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#34">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#34">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#34">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#34">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
