<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Uzbekistan: OMRI-8 OCT 1996--TALIBAN EXTENDING OLIVE BRANCH?</title>
<h1>OMRI-8 OCT 1996--TALIBAN EXTENDING OLIVE BRANCH?</h1>
<i>kkhalmatov@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Wed, 09 Oct 96 11:04:59 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#32">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#32">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#32">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#32">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0033.html">kkhalmatov@sorosny.org: "OMRI--9 OCT 1996--MAYLI-SUU CLEANUP PLANNED"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0031.html">eurasia@sorosny.org: "OMRI -- Oct 9 1996 -- MAYLI-SUU CLEANUP PLANNED"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
