<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Uzbekistan: OMRI--4 OCT 1996--ALMATY PREPARES FOR CIS SUMMIT</title>
<h1>OMRI--4 OCT 1996--ALMATY PREPARES FOR CIS SUMMIT</h1>
<i>kkhalmatov@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Mon, 07 Oct 96 10:16:56 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#30">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#30">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#30">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#30">[ author ]</a>
