<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0031.html">eurasia@sorosny.org: "OMRI -- Oct 9 1996 -- MAYLI-SUU CLEANUP PLANNED"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0029.html">eurasia@sorosny.org: "Human Rights Watch--OSCE Forum Masks Censorship"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
