     DEPUTY MINISTER SLAIN IN UZBEKISTAN. Deputy Communications Minister <br>
     Vladimir Kravchenko was killed at his home on 24 September, ITAR-TASS <br>
     reported. No motive or suspects have been identified. Kravchenko died <br>
     after being stabbed six times. -- Lowell Bezanis<br>
