<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Uzbekistan: OMRI--23 September 96--KAZAK-KYRGYZ-UZBEK TRINITY?</title>
<h1>OMRI--23 September 96--KAZAK-KYRGYZ-UZBEK TRINITY?</h1>
<i>tlankina@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Mon, 23 Sep 96 16:09:49 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#24">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#24">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#24">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#24">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0025.html">tlankina@sorosny.org: "OMRI--25 September 96--DEPUTY MINISTER SLAIN IN UZBEKISTAN"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0023.html">tlankina@sorosny.org: "OMRI--23 September 96--DRAFT LAW ON POLITICAL PARTIES PUBLIS"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
