<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Uzbekistan: OMRI--18 September 96--UZBEKISTAN HOSTS AFGHAN TALKS</title>
<h1>OMRI--18 September 96--UZBEKISTAN HOSTS AFGHAN TALKS</h1>
<i>tlankina@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Wed, 18 Sep 96 12:39:40 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#21">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#21">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#21">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#21">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
