<h1>OMRI--29 August 96--UZBEKISTAN'S CENTRAL BANK CUTS REFINANCI</h1>
<i>tlankina@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Fri, 30 Aug 96 09:21:22 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#12">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#12">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#12">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#12">[ author ]</a>
