<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Uzbekistan: OMRI--23 August 96--NIYAZOV HOSTS UZBEK DEFENSE CHIEF</title>
<h1>OMRI--23 August 96--NIYAZOV HOSTS UZBEK DEFENSE CHIEF</h1>
<i>tlankina@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Fri, 23 Aug 96 12:52:57 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#9">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#9">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#9">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#9">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
