<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0008.html">tlankina@sorosny.org: "OMRI--23 August 96--CASH WITHDRAWALS HALTED IN TASHKENT"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
</ul>
<!-- body="start" -->
     NIYAZOV HOSTS UZBEK DEFENSE CHIEF. Turkmen President Saparmurad <br>
     Niyazov held talks with visiting Uzbek Defense Minister Rustam Ahmedov <br>
     on 20 August, Turkmen Press news agency reported the following day. <br>
     According to the BBC monitored report, the two sides discussed <br>
     cooperation between the Turkmen and Uzbek armed forces. -- Lowell <br>
     Bezanis<br>
<!-- body="end" -->
<p>
