<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Uzbekistan: OMRI--21 August 96--KAMILOV IN NEW DELHI</title>
<h1>OMRI--21 August 96--KAMILOV IN NEW DELHI</h1>
<i>tlankina@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Wed, 21 Aug 96 10:02:52 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#7">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#7">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#7">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#7">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0008.html">tlankina@sorosny.org: "OMRI--23 August 96--CASH WITHDRAWALS HALTED IN TASHKENT"</a>
