<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Uzbekistan: OMRI--15 August 96--UZBEKISTAN'S AIRPORTS TO BE UPGRADED</title>
<h1>OMRI--15 August 96--UZBEKISTAN'S AIRPORTS TO BE UPGRADED</h1>
<i>tlankina@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Thu, 15 Aug 96 12:05:21 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#3">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#3">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#3">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#3">[ author ]</a>
