<PRE>2 Points of Mutual Interest:

1.  I believe the ESL Tutor Project envelops the aims and 
mission of the Soros Foundation, specifically the objectives
of the Emma Lazarus Fund. I would like more information on 
how to apply for a grant.

2.  This past summer, I started the International
Partnership for Corporate Volunteerism, an initiative now
adopted by the Points of Light Foundation with the focus to i
involve the private sector, on a global level, in community 
development projects,through volunteerism and philanthropy.  
We are currently focused in Latin America but will expand 
to Eastern Europe in the near future and are in need of a 
contact non-profit organization in the region. This 
opportunity could be of great interest and benefit to the 
Soros Foundation, as we are in contact with multinational 
corporations who wish to invest in Hungary and other 
emerging markets and can contribute to the region's economic
and social development.  Please contact me to continue the
exchange of information and take the next step together.

In all, great website.  Thanks for reinforcing a personal
belief:

Every individual, internally motived by a balance 
of self-interest and altruism, can contribute to the 
development and advancement of the whole.

</PRE>
