<PRE>I searched for the Website after reading "Philanthropist Pledges
Millions For Immigrants" in USA Today and referring back to the 
Wall Street Journal Article from July 31, 1996, "Study Finds Half 
of Farm Workers Are Illegal". I am presently trying to organize 
citizenship classes in South Carolina.

I would like to thank Mr. Soros for supporting the immigrant 
community in this country. Over the past couple of years and in
this election year in particular, they have been unfairly 
maligned and used as scapegoats for the political gain of 
elected officials in both the Democrat and Republican parties. 
However, maybe the politicians have, in fact, done the immigrant
community a favor, by making them aware of exactly how little 
