<HR>
<A NAME="ruut+brandsma"><B>Ruut Brandsma</B></A><BR>
<I>brandsma@fys.ruu.nl</I><BR>
Netherlands	 - USIC<BR>
 - vice-president<BR>
<A HREF="http://www.fys.ruu.nl/~brandsma">just my bookmarks</A><BR>
NGO	 - USIC is an abriviation for Utrecht Students In Contact. It was found in september 1995. We want to organise personal contacts between students in NL and ex-Yugoslavia, to bring the different 'ethnic' groups in contact with each other, to initiate within these contacts discussions about things like: democracy, peace and the meaning of ethnicity. We have now contacts with the university of Tuzla, and we want to realize our goals at the lowest possible grass-root level. We want to reintegrate an isolated area, show our solidarity to individual students and make the war and violence more concrete to the students in Utrecht, via confrontation with individual experiences. USIC works in a form which is based on mutual respect and equality with its partners, for more info please contact me.
<BR>
WEB SURFING	 - via FREE PRESS NOW! (they have had an action week in NL)
<BR>
Programs of Interest:  FORCED MIGRATION PROJECTS : HIGHER EDUCATION SUPPORT PROGRAM : REGIONAL PROGRAMS FOR CHILDREN AND TEENS :<BR>
<BR>
Countries of Interest:  BOSNIA : CROATIA : YUGOSLAVIA :<BR>
<PRE>great inititaive</PRE>
Signed on: Mon May  6 07:28:03 EDT 1996<BR>

