<a name="drug"></a>
<center><b>DRUG USE AS A SOCIAL RITUAL</b></center>
<p>
Contents<br>
<a href="#use">Social Drug Use and Social Structure</a><br>
<a href="#ill">The Social Structure of Illegal Drug Use</a><br>
<a href="#rule">Social Rituals and Rules Surrounding Group Drug Use</a><br>
